name: YoOoNGZ #12
description:
☆ ☆ ☆ They are not what you think they are.


One night I was playing at this party as a headliner. I got the best hour of the line up. I played a great set, the crowd was amazing, dancefloor jam packed all the time I was up there.

As soon as I got off the booth, I went to the restroom to take a leak. There were 6-10 dudes in there. I got near the urinal, pulled my P out and started to pee.  I suddenly felt my butt being caressed by a strange hand. A hot breath reached my neck and a sound went trough my left ear:

“Hey, handsome. Do you need any help?”
